{
  "stem": "26447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Germans begin-- the police was telling, if they will find something about who keep some-- a Jew or give food or what, we will kill them and them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some people stopped to give us some food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't stop to give it to all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was times what we came at nighttime to people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They make potatoes for the pigs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's not-- they didn't take off the skin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "With the ground, for pigs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they give us, we stay with him and we eat, maybe, a half box or-- that's the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, the stomach becomes like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Doesn't-- it's terrible and hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in not ten minutes, you are again hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We ate some [? flour ?] with water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mix-- we ate like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't got no-- now, it's episodes to tell us every day's episodes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And behind this, what you don't have enough to eat in that situation, morality is-- you're dead-- you know what somebody can kill you, somebody can-- something happen that-- and how it's bad, this life.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "How it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "How a person want to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And to make, maybe-- sometimes, I remind [? myself ?] how many times he was talking with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, it become worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I tell you like-- in that time that we was in the forest-- what we went-- we didn't got-- it was a lot of lice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Excuse me, please.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A lot of lice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We didn't-- the skin-- you cannot find one place what is without blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All the body is in blood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it's terrible, but you have-- it's unbearable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Sometimes, I remember now, when we come sometimes to people at nighttime to ask for a piece of bread or to eat or what.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
